{
  "lines": [
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "1267 年的波兰。圣剑骑士团守护「千年之心」千年。",
      "expression": "normal"
    },
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "如今它被分成了 7 块碎片，散落在王国的 7 处禁地。",
      "expression": "normal"
    },
    {
      "character": "Greyr1",
      "text": "你终于来了... 骑士。",
      "expression": "angry"
    },
    {
      "character": "Greyr1",
      "text": "千年之心已经破碎，你还要追寻吗？",
      "expression": "angry"
    },
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "我会集齐碎片。圣物必须回归。",
      "expression": "determined"
    },
    {
      "character": "Greyr1",
      "text": "那你也会有代价的... 就像我一样。",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Greyr1",
      "text": "既然你选择遗忘，那就来战吧！",
      "expression": "angry"
    }
  ]
}